title: Love & Fetty Wap

description:
TUE 8/23 - Masika from Love & Hip-Hop Hollywood joins The Breakfast Club to talk about her relationship & child with Fetty Wap, her domestic issues with Yung Berg and why her name is attached to Drake, Bieber, Floyd & more. Oh yeah, she's an artist too...we'll get to that.
